REFERENCE DOCUMENTATION ONLY -- NOT A BUILD INPUT.

This unified diff shows **only the filter customization** we add on
top of upstream's Cloud_Spanner_Change_Streams_to_PubSub template --
a single Filter step that drops change records whose every mod has
payload_link NULL on both sides. Malformed records pass through so
the downstream reconciler / DLQ surface them.

Scope caveat: our pipeline diverges from upstream in more ways than
this diff attempts to express -- sink shape, JSON wire format,
dropped options, no Runner V2 injection, no Avro, and more. See the
"Beyond the filter: other differences from upstream" section in
README.md for a full prose enumeration, or run
`./generate-full-delta.sh` to produce the complete diff on demand
against the pinned upstream SHA.

If upstream's pipeline shape evolves and this reference diverges
from our src/ tree, regenerate against a fresh clone of upstream to
keep the reference accurate. See README.md for the procedure. The
SHA in upstream.txt is the upstream commit this diff was last
reviewed against; the diff was verified to apply cleanly
(`git apply --check`) against that revision when captured.

